Overview [#overview]
********************
'afSlim' is a library for generating HTML from lightweight templates.

Based on [Jade]`http://jade-lang.com/` for javascript and [Slim]`http://slim-lang.com/` for Ruby, 'afSlim' generates HTML from
concise, lightweight templates. Features include:

 - No closing tags, use indentation instead
 - Use '#' shortcut for IDs
 - Use '.' shortcut for classes
