Quick Start [#quickStart]
*************************
pre>
doctype html
html
  head
    title afSlim Example
    meta name="keywords" content="fantom html template language"
    script (type="text/javascript")
      alert("Hello ${name}");

  body
    h1 Slim Example

    p This is what a basic Slim file looks like.

    div#content This div has an ID of 'content'
    div.content This div has a class of 'content'

    div (style="color: red;") Specify attributes in brackets

    div[style="color: blue;"] You can also use [square] and {curly} brackets
      p Use indentation...
        span ...to nest tags

    // The is a Slim comment
    /! This is a HTML comment

